high_descs: Turn around and go near the countertop.
Take the knife from the microwave oven.
Turn around and go near the lemon table.
There is a lemon on the sink tray.
Cut the fruit into pieces using the knife on the sink.
Then put the knife into the sink.
Take the piece of fruit from the sink.
Turn around and go near the lemon.
Put the piece of fruit into the sink.
Washed the lemon into the sink.
Take it out and go near the fridge.
Put the lemon into the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around, leave the room from the upper left corner, then head to the opposite corner of the new room and in front of the countertop.
Take the knife out of the microwave.
Turn around and approach the left side of a lemon sink.
Cut the lemon at the sink with the knife.
Step to the right side of the sink.
Place the knife in the sink.
Take a step back where you cut the lemon on the sink.
Pick up the lemon slice from next to the sink.
Take a step right again to be directly in front of the sink.
Put the lemon slice in the sink, rinse the lemon out, then take the lemon back out.
Turn around and walk to the fridge on the left side of your view.
Put the lemon slice in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put the sliced piece of Lemon in the Fridge.

high_descs: Turn right and go towards the wall, then right out of the room onto the countertop, approaching the microwave.
Pick up the knife from the microwave.
Turn around and head towards the lemon on the counters next to the sink.
Cut the closest lemon on the panel to the left of the sink.
Approach the sink basin.
Place the knife down in the sink.
Turn to the sliced lemon in the sink again.
Pick up a slice of lemon from the plate.
Turn to the sink again.
Place the lemon slice in the sink basin and wash the lemon with water before picking it back up.
Turn around to the fridge.
Place the lemon slice in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed Lemon slice in a Fridge.
